BSPs on base of Freescales`s Yocto BSP:
====================================== 
  
  Release: imx-3.10.17-1.0.0_ga_test
  
  1)Setup Build Environment
    Some dependencies are needed for Yocto itself, for more information, 
    see “Yocto Project Quick Start”.

    $ sudo apt-get install gawk wget git-core diffstat unzip texinfo gcc-multilib 
    $ sudo apt-get install build-essential chrpath libsdl1.2-dev xterm libcurl4-openssl-dev lzop curl

    $ mkdir ~/bin
    $ curl http://commondatastorage.googleapis.com/git-repo-downloads/repo > ~/bin/repo
    $ chmod a+x ~/bin/repo
    $ PATH=${PATH}:~/bin

  2)Yocto Environment Initialization
  
    $ mkdir fslbsp
    $ cd fslbsp
    $ fslbsp$ repo init -u git://github.com/gandrys/fsl-imx-yocto-bsp.git -b imx-3.10.17-1.0.0_ga_test
    $ fslbsp$ repo sync
    $ fslbsp$ SDKMACHINE=`uname -m`;MACHINE=imx6dlsabreauto source fsl-setup-release.sh -b build-base
    $ fslbsp/build-base$ bitbake core-image-base
